The paper discusses Ontology-Mediated Query Answering (OMQA) which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions DLs (Description Logics) which are a subfield of knowledge representation and reasoning, falling under cs.LO. Additionally, the paper discusses complexity for query answering which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper mentions SPARQL which is a query language for RDF data, falling under cs.DL.
